Description: Software for fitting Bayesian Polya-gamma regression
    models including multinomial regression, multinomial spatial
    regression, mutlinomial spatially varying coefficient models,
    multinomial spatio-temporal regression models, sparse
    multiresolution multinomial spatial models, and possibly more to come.
